                        <placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/INS0091AQM">ʾAgärhǝse ʾAbuna Mammas / AQM</placeName>
                     </origPlace>
                     <origDate notBefore="1708" notAfter="1711">The colophon mentions Tewoflos (r.
                        1708-11) as King and ʾabbā Marqos as the Metropolitan of Ethiopia (in tenure
                        1689-1716). The Ms. was commissioned by ʾabbā Mikāʾel (a brother of the scribe Misaʾel)
                        "from the house of  ʾabbā Mäṭaʿ", i.e.,
                        probably, from the monastery of Dabra Libānos of Šimezana (Ham).</origDate>
                  </origin>
